1 0 0 1 54 728 Tm
(TuneBridge) Tj
T*
(End-User Install Guide \(macOS\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(What you need) Tj
T*
(- A Mac \(Apple Silicon\)) Tj
T*
(- The file: TuneBridge.dmg) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Install TuneBridge) Tj
T*
(1. Double-click TuneBridge.dmg.) Tj
T*
(2. In the window that opens, drag TuneBridge.app into Applications.) Tj
T*
(3. Open Applications and launch TuneBridge.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Important) Tj
T*
(- Always run TuneBridge from Applications.) Tj
T*
(- Do not run it directly from the DMG window.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If macOS shows a security warning on first launch) Tj
T*
(You may see a message that TuneBridge cannot be verified. This is expected for the current) Tj
T*
(build.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Use this once:) Tj
T*
(1. Go to Applications.) Tj
T*
(2. Right-click TuneBridge.app.) Tj
T*
(3. Click Open.) Tj
T*
(4. In the popup, click Open again.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If it is still blocked) Tj
T*
(1. Open System Settings.) Tj
T*
(2. Go to Privacy & Security.) Tj
T*
(3. Find the TuneBridge blocked-app message.) Tj
T*
(4. Click Open Anyway.) Tj
T*
(5. Launch TuneBridge again from Applications.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(First run setup) Tj
T*
(When TuneBridge opens for the first time:) Tj
T*
(1. Choose your music library folder.) Tj
T*
(2. Confirm your folder/file preferences.) Tj
T*
(3. Continue into the app.) Tj
T*
() Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
3 0 obj
<< /Length 631 >>
stream
BT
/F1 12 Tf
17 TL
1 0 0 1 54 728 Tm
(Where TuneBridge saves your data) Tj
T*
(TuneBridge stores your library/playlists/settings here:) Tj
T*
(~/Library/Application Support/TuneBridge) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Updating to a newer TuneBridge build) Tj
T*
(1. Download the new TuneBridge.dmg.) Tj
T*
(2. Drag the new TuneBridge.app to Applications.) Tj
T*
(3. Replace the old app when macOS asks.) Tj
T*
(4. Open TuneBridge.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Your app data remains in Application Support and is kept between updates.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Need help?) Tj
T*
(If TuneBridge does not open, restart your Mac and try the first-launch steps again.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
